OL,6,FA third of all recreational players in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales are of South Asian
OL,8,Fdescent, while participation among
OL,9,Fwomen and girls rose by more than a
OL,10,Ffifth in 2024.
OL,12,FThe dome at Farington will open in the
