OL,6,FThe Luton dome, due to open in early
OL,7,F2026, will give state school children
OL,8,Faccess to cricket, with the potential
OL,9,Fto offer other sports, including
OL,10,Fhockey and tennis.
OL,12,FEngland and Lancashire spinner Sophie
OL,13,FEcclestone said: "It's fantastic that
OL,14,Fmore people will get the chance to
OL,15,Fplay cricket thanks to these brilliant
OL,16,Fdomes.
