OL,3,CNew domes to allow cricket to be
OL,4,Cplayed year round
OL,6,F"Facilities like these can make a
OL,7,Fmassive difference in local
OL,8,Fcommunities and open cricket up to so
OL,9,Fmany more people, and it will be
OL,10,Fbrilliant to see them in action next
OL,11,Fyear."
OL,13,FSecretary of State for Culture, Media
OL,14,Fand Sport, Lisa Nandy, said: "Cricket
OL,15,Fhas a remarkable power to inspire and
OL,16,Funite communities all over the world
OL,17,Fand today we are making sure that more
OL,18,Fpeople of all backgrounds have the
OL,19,Fchance to experience the game.
