OL,3,CNew domes to allow cricket to be
OL,4,Cplayed year round
OL,6,F"These domes will be places where
OL,7,Fcricket-lovers and newcomers alike can
OL,8,Fcome together to play, get active,
OL,9,Fmake real-life connections and chase
OL,10,Fsporting dreams."
OL,12,FOfficials hope the domes will help to
OL,13,Fsmooth the road from grassroots to the
OL,14,Ftop of the game, allowing boys and
OL,15,Fgirls to be inspired by cricketing
OL,16,Fstars such as Ben Stokes and Lauren
OL,17,FBell.
