OL,4,Cplayed year round
OL,6,FECB chair Richard Thompson said:
OL,7,F"These state-of-the-art all-weather
OL,8,Fcricket domes will be transformative
OL,9,Ffor the communities they serve,
OL,10,Fopening up cricket to more people year-
OL,11,Fround and providing top-class
OL,12,Ffacilities for elite players too.
OL,14,F"They are an important part of our
OL,15,Fplans to break down barriers and make
OL,16,Fcricket the most inclusive team sport.
